4. What are the key challenges facing the LAA occluder market?
Reimbursement issues, stringent regulatory approvals, and the high cost of LAA occluder devices are some of the challenges facing the market.

5. What are the major players in the global LAA occluder market?
Some of the key players in the market include Boston Scientific Corporation, Abbott Laboratories, and AtriCure, Inc.

