As of 2021, Boston Scientific Corporation held the largest market share, followed by Abbott Laboratories and AtriCure, Inc.

10. What are the regulatory requirements for LAA occluder devices?
LAA occluder devices are regulated by the FDA in the United States and by the CE Mark in Europe.

